snippet: Reflecting a highly uncertain and divided outlook on monetary policy, regional Federal Reserve banks supported three options for the discount rate last month.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON (Dow Jones/AP)  Reflecting a highly uncertain and divided outlook on monetary policy, regional Federal Reserve banks supported three options for the discount rate last month, according to minutes of the December meeting of the Federal Open Market Committee, released Tuesday.

headline.main: Fed Panel Was Divided Over Outlook for Economy
